	PROCEDURE about		&& Provides documentation for the class.
		*==============================================================================
		* Class:					SFShape
		* Based On:					Shape
		* Purpose:					The base class for all Shape objects
		* Author:					Doug Hennig
		* Copyright:				(c) 1996-2002 Stonefield Systems Group Inc.
